, \"from\": 354, \"to\": 362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Except ... did the stoic rider from Ecuador actually crack a smile?\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador\", \"score\": 0.9999999991246113, \"rank\": 7.101725630280143e-10, \"text\": \"Ecuador\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stoic rider\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"a smile\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, he did.\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That same stunt that overzealous fans pull in the Alps and Pyrenees during the Tour de France, where it might annoy Carapaz to no end, was actually welcomed by him in the Olympic road race.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 528, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999603368281721, \"rank\": 2.8718750766952897e-05, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That same stunt\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"overzealous fans\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"the Alps\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"Pyrenees\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 516}, {\"ngram\": \"Carapaz\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"no end\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic road race\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's because the draconian measures taken by the organizers of the Tokyo Games to prevent the spread of COVID-19 have also prevented fans from the once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to see most of the world's best athletes perform on their own soil.\", \"from\": 639, \"t